data.description: This charming rambler/ranch is nestled in a peaceful neighborhood. The perfect home for those seeking main floor, single story living. This inviting residence boasts a one-car attached garage and a fenced-in yard. This home has a new roof and tankless on-demand hot water. The interior is designed for comfort and functionality, featuring a large laundry room with built-in storage. The spacious kitchen is complemented by a sunny dining room that bathes in natural light. Three well-sized bedrooms are adorned with the beautiful original hardwood flooring. Make this property your haven and embrace the comfort of a well-appointed home. Schedule a showing with your favorite agent today.
